msgctxt "484_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Oh, glad you're back! They've been hissing at us\\r\n"\n"something awful, and they won't even let us look\\r\n"\n"at their injuries."
msgstr "¡Oh, me alegro hayas vuelto! Nos han estado gruñendo\\r\n"\n"horriblemente, y ni siquier nos dejan verles\\r\n"\n"sus heridas."

msgctxt "496_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "We've got to hurry or they'll be in really bad shape.\\r\n"\n"Please try to tame them!"
msgstr "Tenemos que darnos prisa o se pondrán muy mal.\\r\n"\n"¡Por favor hazte amigo de ellos!"

msgctxt "508_Saejima"
msgid "Tamin' cats, huh?"
msgstr "Hacerme amigo de los gatos, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "520_Saejima"
msgid "Sorry, but it ain't gonna happen. Just not big on cats."
msgstr "Lo lamento, pero no va a pasar. No soy mucho de gatos."

msgctxt "532_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "You sure? Oh, all right then."
msgstr "¿Seguro? Oh, está bien entonces."

msgctxt "544_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Bah! Then give us some space and get lost!"
msgstr "¡Bah! ¡Entonces danos espacio y vete de aquí!"

msgctxt "556_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "We're going to stay put until these cats are okay..."
msgstr "Nos quedaremos aquí hasta que estos gatos estén bien..."

msgctxt "640_Saejima"
msgid "Alright, why the hell not?"
msgstr "Está bien, ¿Por qué carajos no lo haría?"

msgctxt "652_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Great! We're counting on you!"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¡Contamos contigo!"

msgctxt "712_Striped Kitten"
msgid "Hssst!"
msgstr "¡Hsst!"

msgctxt "724_Saejima"
msgid "(Little fella's really givin' me what for. Now what do I do?)"
msgstr "(El pequeñín de verdad me las está poniendo difícil. ¿Qué hago ahora?)"

msgctxt "736_Saejima"
msgid "(Maybe these cats grew up in a pet shop with dogs. I'll try barkin'.)"
msgstr "(Quizás estos gatitos se criaron en una tienda de mascotas junto a los perros. Intentaré ladrarles.)"

msgctxt "748_Saejima"
msgid "Rrr..."
msgstr "Rrr..."

msgctxt "760_Striped Kitten"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "772_Saejima"
msgid "Woof! Arf, arf!"
msgstr "¡Guau! ¡Arf, arf!"

msgctxt "784_Striped Kitten"
msgid "Ffft! Ffft!"
msgstr "¡Ffft! ¡Ffft!"

msgctxt "796_Saejima"
msgid "(Now it's even more pissed off.)"
msgstr "(Ahora está aún más enojado.)"

msgctxt "820_Saejima"
msgid "(Maybe these kitties'll open to me if I act like a sweet little crying girl.)"
msgstr "(Quizás estos gatitos abrirán su corazón si actuo como una niñita llorando.)"

msgctxt "832_Saejima"
msgid "Ugh..."
msgstr "Ugh..."

msgctxt "844_Striped Kitten"
msgid "Mew?"
msgstr "¿Miau?"

msgctxt "856_Saejima"
msgid "Nah, fuck it. Lemme try again."
msgstr "Nah, A la mierda. Déjenme volver a intentarlo."

msgctxt "880_Saejima"
msgid "(Prolly oughta try speakin' their own language.)"
msgstr "(A lo mejor debería intentar hablar su mismo idioma.)"

msgctxt "892_Saejima"
msgid "Mmm..."
msgstr "Mmm..."

msgctxt "904_Striped Kitten"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "916_Saejima"
msgid "...Meow."
msgstr "...Miau."

msgctxt "928_Striped Kitten"
msgid "Meow..."
msgstr "Miau..."

msgctxt "940_Saejima"
msgid "(Seems like it finally dropped its guard.)"
msgstr "(Parece que por fin bajó la guardia.)"

msgctxt "952_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Wow, you're good. Poor things wouldn't even give me\\r\n"\n"the time of day."
msgstr "Wow, eres bueno. Pobrecitos ni siquiera me darían\\r\n"\n"la hora en la calle."

msgctxt "964_Saejima"
msgid "They don't look like they're doing too good."
msgstr "No parece que les esté yendo muy bien."

msgctxt "976_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "We gotta get some nutrition into these little guys."
msgstr "Tenemos que nutrir un poco a estos pequeñines."

msgctxt "988_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Bah. A drink'd patch 'em right up."
msgstr "Bue. Un trago los arreglará de inmediato."

msgctxt "1000_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "I hate to ask, but could you buy these kittens something\\r\n"\n"you think they'd like?"
msgstr "Odio pedirlo, pero ¿podrías comprarle algo que les guste\\r\n"\n"a estos gatitos?"

msgctxt "1012_Saejima"
msgid "(S'pose I can't back out now. I'll get 'em somethin' real nutritious, like... fuck, I dunno.)"
msgstr "(Supongo que ya no me puedo echar para atrás. Les conseguiré algo muy nutritivo, algo como... mierda, no lo sé.)"

msgctxt "1024_Saejima"
msgid "Wait here. Ya gotta offer lost cats some milk.\\r\n"\n"I'll go pick some up."
msgstr "Esperen aquí. Tienen que darles algo de leche.\\r\n"\n"Iré a comprar una."

msgctxt "1108_Saejima"
msgid "Wait here. I'll buy somethin' to perk 'em up.\\r\n"\n"They're hurt, so maybe Staminan X?"
msgstr "Esperen aquí. Iré algo para energizarlos.\\r\n"\n"Están heridos, ¿así que quizás les traigo un Staminan X?"

msgctxt "1192_Saejima"
msgid "Wait here. Doesn't matter what cats eat.\\r\n"\n"They prolly wouldn't say no to dog food."
msgstr "Esperen aquí. No importa lo que coman los gatos.\\r\n"\n"Así que a lo mejor les da igual la comida de perro."

msgctxt "1264_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "Here, kitty-kitty! We got some fish for you!"
msgstr "¡Gatito, gatito! ¡Toma un poco de pescado!"

msgctxt "1276_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Want some beer...? Huh! Darn things just won't warm up to me."
msgstr "¿O quieres un poco de cerveza? ¡Agh!\\r\n"\n"Estas cosas no me agradan."

msgctxt "1288_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Aw, you guys aren't seeing cat's eye to cat's eye with them.\\r\n"\n"Watch and learn."
msgstr "Aggh, no están entendiendo los sentimientos del gato.\\r\n"\n"Miren y aprendan."

msgctxt "1300_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Mrowrrr."
msgstr "Miaaau."

msgctxt "1312_Striped Kitten"
msgid "Ffft!"
msgstr "¡Ffft!"

msgctxt "1324_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Yeah, I didn't think so."
msgstr "Sí, creo que no está funcionando."

msgctxt "1336_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "That's odd. My old cat Miko would always come right up to me when I did that."
msgstr "Qué raro... Mi viejo gato Miko venía\\r\n"\n"siempre que le hacía así."

msgctxt "1348_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "If they won't let us touch them, we can't check their injuries, and we can't fix them up."
msgstr "Si no nos dejas tocarte,\\r\n"\n"no podremos ayudarte."

msgctxt "1360_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "Hmm?"
msgstr "¿Mmm?"

msgctxt "1372_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Huh? What are you lookin' at?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Qué estás mirando?"

msgctxt "1384_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "Hey, take it easy fellas. Say, pal, are you a cat lover?"
msgstr "Oye, no seas así, ¿qué tal?\\r\n"\n"¿Te gustan los gatos?"

msgctxt "1396_Saejima"
msgid "Cats, huh?"
msgstr "Gatos..."

msgctxt "1408_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "You are? That's great! Can you do something about these cats?"
msgstr "¿Te gustan los gatos? ¡Genial!\\r\n"\n"¿Podrías hacer algo por ellos, amigo?"

msgctxt "1420_Saejima"
msgid "Whoa there. I didn't say I was a cat lover."
msgstr "No he dicho nada aún..."

msgctxt "1432_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "Ah, that's okay. Anyway, we just found these little guys, but unfortunately they're not letting any of us touch 'em."
msgstr "Bueno, no te preocupes por los detalles.\\r\n"\n"Acabamos de encontrar a estos pequeños, pero aún no nos dejan tocarlos."

msgctxt "1444_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, but－"
msgstr "Pero－"

msgctxt "1468_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "They look like they're hurt. We only wanna patch them up if we can."
msgstr "Parecen heridos, mínimo deberíamos cuidarlos."

msgctxt "1480_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "It must be fate, you showing up like this. Could you try taming these little fellas?"
msgstr "¿Qué dices? Tiene que ser el destino.\\r\n"\n"¿No podrías intentar hacerte amigo de ellos?"

msgctxt "1492_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Yeah, please? If we don't act fast, they'll get weaker and weaker. You're our only hope－and theirs!"
msgstr "Te lo ruego. Si no lo haces pronto, estos pequeños se debilitarán más, ¡confiamos en ti!, ¡eres nuestra única esperanza!"

msgctxt "1504_Saejima"
msgid "Ya want me to tame a buncha cats, huh?"
msgstr "¿Hacerme amigo de estos gatos...?"

msgctxt "1516_Saejima"
msgid "Ain't gonna happen. Sorry, but I ain't big on the furballs."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no me llevo bien con los gatos."

msgctxt "1528_Friendly Homeless Man"
msgid "You're not? Oh, well."
msgstr "Entiendo, no hay problema entonces."

msgctxt "1540_Surly Homeless Man"
msgid "Bah! Then quit wasting our time!"
msgstr "¡Bah! ¡Entones no nos hagas perder el tiempo!"

msgctxt "1552_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "We're not budging until these cats are safe and sound."
msgstr "No nos moveremos de aquí hasta que estos gatos estén sanos y salvos."

msgctxt "1636_Saejima"
msgid "Alright, why the hell not? Guess I'll see what I can do."
msgstr "Bien, ¿Por qué no? Veré lo que puedo hacer."

msgctxt "1648_Cat-loving Homeless Man"
msgid "Great! We're counting on you!"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¡Contamos contigo!"

